worker/src/web.mjs:44:    ['发网页，而不只是发文件','Share a web page, not just a file'],['接收者打开就能看，分享者保留对展示方式、下载入口和有效期的控制。','Recipients can read immediately while you retain control over presentation, downloads, and lifetime.'],['减少打开阻力','Remove opening friction'],['方案、报告和演示稿无需先下载，也不要求对方安装 Word、PowerPoint 或其他应用。','Plans, reports, and decks open without a download or Word, PowerPoint, and other apps.'],['适合审阅与交付','Made for review and delivery'],['关闭下载入口并添加文字水印，让页面更适合客户审阅、内部评审和阶段性交付。水印用于归属提示，不等同于 DRM。','Disable the download action and add a text watermark for client review, internal feedback, and staged delivery. A watermark signals ownership; it is not DRM.'],['生命周期清楚','Clear lifecycle'],['文件按所选有效期安全保存；到期后链接停止访问并自动清理，登录用户也可以创建长期分享。','Files are kept securely for the selected lifetime. Expired links stop working and are cleaned up automatically; signed-in users can also create persistent shares.'],
